title: GoHealth Urgent Care
description:
Experience a new standard of urgent care.

Open our door and experience a new level of urgent care – one that’s advanced, comfortable and staffed with highly qualified providers from the leading local hospital system. They’re equipped to handle everything from kitchen burns to sprains, fevers to UTIs, allergies, ear infections, insect bites and more.

Seamless connections to specialty care.

If a provider should find you may need care beyond your visit, we can refer you to a local specialist through our partnerships with a highly rated health system in your area, so you can get all the care you need without long waits or wondering where to go.

Manage your health on the go with our new free app.

Use our new app to locate a center near you, save your spot in line or schedule a Virtual Visit, which is usually available the same day. All our providers have telemedicine training, so you’ll get the same high-quality care you would in one of our centers. Walk-ins are also welcome!

Our partners:
